Roccat has revealed pricing for its Leadr wireless gaming mouse, aimed at hardcore PC gamers. The Leadr was announced at CES 2017 and boasts: Roccat said the mouse features almost identical accuracy when used in a wired or wireless set-up. A charging dock is included with the mouse, which features a 20-hour battery life, RGB lighting zones, and 14 programmable buttons The Leadr gaming mouse is available to pre-order from Roccat’s website for $140.    